  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个流程图，展示患者从社区到住院，再到出院受阻的完整路径。核心是解释为什么急诊会拥堵——不是因为前面环节慢，而是出院环节卡住了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "ED_Arrival",
        "Inpatient",
        "Ready",
        "Block_Aged",
        "Block_NDIS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，这是一个\"入院容易出院难\"的模型。起点是社区，然后经过GP或者急诊到达？我需要确认一下入口设计。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "GP",
        "ED_Arrival"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，患者可以从社区直接去急诊，或者先看GP再由GP转诊到急诊。这两条路径都要保留。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "GP",
        "ED_Arrival"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把社区作为最左侧起点，分出两条线：一条到GP/primary care，另一条直接到ED arrival。GP那边再连到ED arrival。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "GP",
        "ED_Arrival"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "急诊部分要分两步：先到诊（ED arrival），然后是评估治疗（ED assessment & treatment）。这是两个不同的状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ED_Arrival",
        "ED_Treat"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加ED arrival和ED assessment & treatment，从左到右串联。接下来是入院决策？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ED_Arrival",
        "ED_Treat",
        "Admission"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，评估治疗后有一个决策点——决定是否收治入院。这个节点本身不是状态，只是一个决策。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ED_Treat",
        "Admission",
        "Inpatient"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Decision to admit已加入，然后连接到Inpatient stay。住院状态用醒目的颜色标注吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Admission",
        "Inpatient"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "住院状态和急诊治疗状态都用红色系，表示它们是系统的\"占用态\"——床位被占用了。然后要有一个\"Ready for discharge\"节点，表示临床意义上可以出院了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Inpatient",
        "Ready"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Inpatient stay和Ready for discharge都加上了。现在到关键部分了——你说的\"出院受阻\"具体是哪几种blockages？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ready",
        "Block_Aged",
        "Block_NDIS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "两大类：一是老年护理床位短缺（Aged care placement capacity constraint），二是NDIS支持或住宿安排延迟（NDIS supports / accommodation delay）。这两个都是capacity constraint。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_Aged",
        "Block_NDIS",
        "Ready"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这两个阻塞节点是从Ready for discharge分出来的并行路径？还是二选一的关系？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ready",
        "Block_Aged",
        "Block_NDIS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "并行的，一个患者可能同时遇到两种阻塞，也可能是其中一种。所以Ready要同时连到Block_Aged和Block_NDIS。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ready",
        "Block_Aged",
        "Block_NDIS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，两条阻塞路径都画好了。现在最重要的——你提到的\"反馈回路\"怎么体现？这是access block mechanism的核心吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_Aged",
        "Inpatient",
        "ED_Treat"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，这是关键。Block_Aged要有一条虚线连回Inpatient stay，标注\"occupancy feedback loop\"。意思是老年护理卡住导致床位占用，占用又导致新患者进不来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_Aged",
        "Inpatient",
        "occupancy feedback loop"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "虚线反馈回路已添加。还有一个optional的回路你提到吗？关于ED的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_Aged",
        "Inpatient",
        "ED_Treat",
        "high occupancy limits flow"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，建议加上：Inpatient到ED_Treat的虚线，标注\"high occupancy limits flow\"。这样更完整显示拥堵如何倒灌到急诊治疗环节。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Inpatient",
        "ED_Treat",
        "high occupancy limits flow"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "两个反馈回路都画好了。现在需要定义样式：我注意到你想用不同颜色区分节点类型？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "classDef",
        "cth",
        "state",
        "risk",
        "neutral"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
